General.Name: Paragon Union Bhd
General.Description: Paragon Union Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures, sells, and trades in car and commercial carpets, and automotive components in Malaysia, Singapore, Brunei, the United Arab Emirates, and South Korea. It operates through Automotive and Commercial segments. The company offers commercial carpets, such as woven axminster, machine and hand tufted, wilton, and mosque carpets, as well as carpet tiles and rugs for use in 5 star hotels, commercial buildings, offices, mosques, and government projects. It also provides automotive products, carpet mats, insulators/silencers, trim parts, and carpet floors. In addition, the company is involved in the property development activities. The company was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Cheras, Malaysia.
